description:
This week, we’ll speak with Marvel Television’s Ironheart Head Writer and Executive Producer Chinaka Hodge about what to expect from the series. Then, we’ll hear from Executive Creative Director at Walt Disney Imagineering Dan Fields about interacting with your favorite heroes at Avengers Campus. Later on, comics writer Zoe Tunnell discusses her work in Marvel United: A Pride Special #1 (21:37). 

00:00 - Welcome Back!

12:20 - Interacting with heroes on Avengers Campus w/ Executive Creative Director at Walt Disney Imagineering Dan Fields
